parameters:
You're not a devil or anything! Come on, touch
them, Konoha's beloved breasts.

You're not just some perverted king like Leon
DeVille.

More importantly, if you come this far... you
won't be able to go back...!

Go back! Together with you, King Leon! Go back to
Gardis!

(My memories... about my younger brother... were
sealed... Why did something like that...
happen...)

Because you killed \C[3]... my mind... must have
been broken... You couldn't stay sane.

Where are you... Leon! It's so fluffy and hard to
move forward...!

It's futile... Leon made his own choice... Let's
sleep together here... Until we wake up again...
I don't know why, but it feels close...!
